::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::
 Package name: DETAILS
 Short Desc: Template for MODx Revolution
 Version: 0.1 (Revolution compatible)
 Author: 
    Menno Pietersen (designfromwithin.com and nieuwe-website-ontwerpen.nl)
::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::
Description:
    MODx HTML5 Boilerplate based template TV controlled with CSS3, HTML5 and jQuery slider
    format you desire.
::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::
Usage:
    #1 
	- Upload/copy zipped package to: <your_website_root>/core/packages/
	
	#2 
	- Go to MODx Revolution manager
	- Click on: System > Package Management > Add New Package
	- Select 'Search Locally for Packages'
	- Click 'Next'
	- Install the 'DETAILS' add-on
	- Clear you Cache!
